    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JUGGLE STAR DX is meant to be played casually. The point of the game is to keep up a ball and ensure it passes all rings in the level or destroys all end goals. As of now, it contains 30+ levels where you can play with keeping up a ball and later on, juggling multiple balls using the paddle.<br><br>Among the levels included are:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dexterity levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multi-ball levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precision levels</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play it with a <strong>mouse</strong> or <strong>touchscreen</strong>.  <br><br>Other features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Day/night cycle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High rotation audio mechanics</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
